.ident	"@(#)niccfg:help/nic_select	1.1"
.related /dev/null
.title Network Card Summary Help Screen

 Please select which Network Interface Card that is installed in this 
 machine.  If you have multiple cards installed, you must select 
 network cards one at a time.  To select a card, TAB the cursor to 
 the corresponding entry and press ENTER.  To view more choices, use 
 the Page Up/Page Down keys. 
 
 For the extended list of cards supported by each entry, 
 press <F6>. 

 EXITING HELP
 Press <Esc> to return to the Network Interface Card Selection Menu. 
